chunk: Heres to the crazy ones. The misfits. The rebels. The troublemakers. The round pegs in the square ho
The ones who see things differently. Theyre not fond of rules. And they have no respect for the stat
us quo. You can quote them, disagree with them, glorify or vilify them.
About the only thing you cant do is ignore them. Because they change things. They invent. They imagi
ne. They heal. They explore. They create. They inspire. They push the human race forward.
Maybe they have to be crazy.
How else can you stare at an empty canvas and see a work of art? Or sit in silence and hear a song t
hats never been written? Or gaze at a red planet and see a laboratory on wheels?
We make tools for these kinds of people.
While some see them as the crazy ones, we see genius. Because the people who are crazy enough to thi
nk they can change the world, are the ones who do.
